<li><span class="citation book" id="CITEREFWood2011">—— (2011). <i>The Idea of America: Reflections on the Birth of the United States</i>. Penguin Press. <a href="International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="Special_BookSources/978-1-59420-290-2" title="Special:BookSources/978-1-59420-290-2">978-1-59420-290-2</a>.</span></li>
</ul>
