<li>Horn, James P. P. Jan Ellen Lewis, and Peter S. Onuf, eds.(2002) <i>The Revolution of 1800: Democracy, Race, and the New Republic</i> pp.&#160;431, 17 essays by scholars, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://books.google.com/books?id=NB20R1QLyjsC&source=gbs_navlinks_s">Url</a></li>
