<li>Jayne, Allen (2000)<i>Jefferson's Declaration of Independence: Origins, Philosophy and Theology</i>&#160;; traces TJ's sources and emphasizes his incorporation of Deist theology into the Declaration.</li>
<li>Kennedy, Roger G. (2003) <i>Mr. Jefferson's Lost Cause: Land, Farmers, Slavery, and the Louisiana Purchase</i></li>
<li>Knudson, Jerry W. (2006) <i>Jefferson and the Press: Crucible of Liberty.</i></li>
