<span style="font-weight: bold"><a href="Patrick_Henry" title="Patrick Henry">Patrick Henry</a></span></td>
<td width="40%" style="text-align: center;" rowspan="1"><b><a href="Governor_of_Virginia" title="Governor of Virginia">Governor of Virginia</a></b><br />
1779–1781</td>
<td width="30%" align="center" rowspan="1">Succeeded&#160;by<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold"><a href="William_Fleming_(governor)" title="William Fleming (governor)">William Fleming</a></span></td>
